Thank you to everyone that made my 47th so special! 
Yet another wild trip around the sun for this fire dragon Leo! 
This year has been by far the most challenging, full of so many changes and important life lessons. It’s been truly humbling and awakening…The theme over the past year was how to move forward with setting boundaries and learning when and how to let go of anything that no longer serves us/me…Letting go of the energies and people that are weighing us down. 
My focus for my 47th year is to focus on conscious efforts and healthy boundaries. Also to show my love and appreciation to all the beautiful humans in my life! 
Salud, dinero, Amor y tiempo para disfrutarlo!!!

Happy Friday from East Hampton! thank you Helena Blavatsky for these words that have been guiding me through Leo Season!

“Do not be afraid of your difficulties 
Do not wish you can be in other circumstances then you are
For when you have made the best of adversity 
It becomes the stepping stone to a splendid opportunity”

To all you beauties, have an incredible weekend!

Finally back in LA and reflecting on what a great Leo season I had on the East Coast and how much I love a New England Summers!
